import {
  Box,
  Container,
  FormControl,
  FormControlLabel,
  FormHelperText,
  InputLabel,
  TextField,
} from "@material-ui/core"

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="xs">
      
        <form>
          <FormControl>
            <TextField
              variant="outlined"
              margin="normal"
              required
              fullWidth
              id="email"
              label="Email Address"
              name="email"
              autoComplete="email"
              autoFocus
            ></TextField>
          </FormControl>
        </form>
      
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Login
